getOperation

private QName getOperation(SOAPMessage request)
Gets the name of the operation invoked by the request message.

If the operation is a RPC/literal style, then the operation name is the local name of the soap body child element. If it is a Document/literal operation we have to find an operation with an input message with only one part of same element qname as the soap body child element.

As we do not know if the message is in RPC or Document style, we first check to see if there is a matching RPC operation.

Parameters:
request -
Returns:
operation name
